Package com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.typedec

Provides utility interfaces to declare native types.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CallConv The CallConv interface holds the constants defining the native method calling conventionalisms.
CPPClassDescriptor The CPPClassDescriptor interface describes a user defined Java class defined as a C++ class.
NativeBehaviorDescriptor The NativeBehaviorDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of Java methods and field-methods declared as native.
NativeBehaviorSignature The NativeBehaviorSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of all method types.
NativeClassDescriptor The NativeClassDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of all user defined native classes.
NativeConstructorDescriptor The NativeConstructorDescriptor is the descriptor interface of user defined native constructors.
NativeConstructorSignature The NativeConstructorSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of native constructors.
NativeDirectCallbackDescriptor The NativeDirectCallbackDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of direct callback native classes.
NativeDirectConstructorCallbackDescriptor The NativeDirectConstructorCallbackDescriptor interface is the descriptor of direct constructor callback native classes.
NativeDirectFieldCallbackDescriptor The NativeDirectFieldCallbackDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of direct field callback native classes.
NativeDirectInstanceFieldCallbackDescriptor The NativeDirectInstanceFieldCallbackDescriptor interface is the descriptor of direct instance field callback native classes.
NativeDirectInstanceMethodCallbackDescriptor The NativeDirectInstanceMethodCallbackDescriptor interface is the descriptor of direct instance method callback native classes.
NativeDirectMethodCallbackDescriptor The NativeDirectMethodCallbackDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of direct method callback native classes.
NativeDirectStaticFieldCallbackDescriptor The NativeDirectStaticFieldCallbackDescriptor interface is the descriptor of direct static field callback native classes.
NativeDirectStaticMethodCallbackDescriptor The NativeDirectStaticMethodCallbackDescriptor interface is the descriptor of direct static method callback native classes.
NativeFieldContainerDescriptor The NativeFieldContainerDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of "field based" native classes.
NativeFieldDescriptor The NativeFieldDescriptor is the descriptor interface of native fields of user defined native classes.
NativeFieldMethodDescriptor The NativeFieldMethodDescriptor is the descriptor interface of user defined native constructors.
NativeFieldMethodSignature The NativeFieldMethodSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of native field-methods.
NativeFieldStructureDescriptor The NativeFieldStructureDescriptor is the descriptor interface of native fields of user defined native structure and C++ classes.
NativeInstanceFieldMethodSignature The NativeInstanceFieldMethodSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of native instance field-methods.
NativeInstanceMethodSignature The NativeInstanceMethodSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of native instance methods.
NativeMemberDescriptor The NativeMemberDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of Java fields and methods declared as native.
NativeMethodDescriptor The NativeMethodDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of Java methods declared as native.
NativeMethodSignature The NativeMethodSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of native methods.
NativeMultipleFieldContainerDescriptor The NativeMultipleFieldContainerDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of unions and "separated field" containers like C++ classes and structures.
NativeObjectArrayDescriptor The NativeObjectArrayDescriptor interface represents the descriptor of an user defined native capable object array class.
NativeObjectFieldContainerDescriptor The NativeObjectFieldContainerDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of one and only native field user defined classes.
NativeParameterDec The NativeParameterDec interface represents a parameter declaration of a native method signature.
NativePointerDescriptor The NativePointerDescriptor interface represents the descriptor of an user defined pointer wrapper.
NativeSeparatedFieldContainerDescriptor The NativeSeparatedFieldContainerDescriptor interface is the base interface of descriptor interfaces of "separated field" containers like C++ classes and structures.
NativeSignatureManager The NativeSignatureManager is the interface used to declare signatures of native methods.
NativeStaticFieldMethodSignature The NativeStaticFieldMethodSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of static native field-methods.
NativeStaticMethodSignature The NativeStaticMethodSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of static native methods.
NativeTypeManager The NativeTypeManager is the interface used to declare native types using native capable classes (user defined or predefined).
NativeVarTypeManager The NativeVarTypeManager is the interface used to declare native variable types.
StringEncoding The StringEncoding declares the constants used to define the encoding and size of characters of native strings.
StructureDescriptor The StructureDescriptor interface describes a user defined Java class defined as a structure.
TypeCanBeNativeCapable The TypeCanBeNativeCapable is the interface that represents a native type declaration of "can be native" classes and native wrapper classes (user defined and predefined).
TypeNative The TypeNative is the interface that represents a native type declaration using native capable classes (user defined or predefined).
TypeNativeArray The TypeNativeArray is the interface that represents a native array type declaration using a Java array or a predefined array wrapper or a user defined array class.
TypeNativeBehavior The TypeNativeBehavior is the interface that represents a native behavior type declaration.
TypeNativeCapable The TypeNativeCapable is the interface that represents a native type declaration of native (Object based) classes.
TypeNativeConstructor The TypeNativeConstructor is the interface that represents a native constructor type declaration.
TypeNativeFieldMethod The TypeNativeFieldMethod is the interface that represents a native field-method type declaration.
TypeNativeInstanceFieldMethod The TypeNativeInstanceFieldMethod is the interface that represents a native instance field-method type declaration.
TypeNativeInstanceMethod The TypeNativeInstanceMethod is the interface that represents a native instance method type declaration.
TypeNativeLong The TypeNativeLong is the interface that represents a native type declaration using a long type.
TypeNativeMethod The TypeNativeMethod is the interface that represents a native method type declaration.
TypeNativeObject The TypeNativeObject is the interface that represents a native type declaration of Object based classes: "can be native" and native capable classes (predefined and user defined).
TypeNativePointer The TypeNativePointer is the interface that represents a native type declaration of NativePointer based classes (predefined and user defined).
TypeNativePrimitive The TypeNativePrimitive is the interface that represents a native type declaration of a primitive data type (boolean, byte, char, short, int, long, float, double).
TypeNativePrimitiveObject The TypeNativePrimitiveObject is the interface that represents a native type declaration of Java primitive wrappers and related native wrappers like Boolean, NativeBooleanObject, Character, NativeCharacterObject and so on.
TypeNativePrimitiveWrapper The TypeNativePrimitiveWrapper is the interface that represents a native type declaration of native wrappers of primitive types (int is wrapped by NativeInteger etc).
TypeNativeStaticFieldMethod The TypeNativeStaticFieldMethod is the interface that represents a native static field-method type declaration.
TypeNativeStaticMethod The TypeNativeStaticMethod is the interface that represents a native static method type declaration.
TypeNativeString The TypeNativeString is the interface that represents a native type declaration of java.lang.String and related wrapper classes.
TypeNativeStringAnsi The TypeNativeStringAnsi is the interface that represents a native type declaration of NativeStringAnsi.
TypeNativeStringBased The TypeNativeStringBased is the interface that represents a native type declaration of java.lang.String or java.lang.StringBuffer and related wrapper classes.
TypeNativeStringBuffer The TypeNativeStringBuffer is the interface that represents a native type declaration of java.lang.StringBuffer and related wrapper classes.
TypeNativeStringBufferAnsi The TypeNativeStringBufferAnsi is the interface that represents a native type declaration of NativeStringBufferAnsi.
TypeNativeStringBufferUnicode The TypeNativeStringBufferUnicode is the interface that represents a native type declaration of NativeStringBufferUnicode.
TypeNativeStringUnicode The TypeNativeStringUnicode is the interface that represents a native type declaration of NativeStringUnicode.
UnionDescriptor The UnionDescriptor interface describes a user defined Java class defined as a union.
VarTypeNative The native variable type is the interface that represents a native declaration of a field member of a native structure/class/union or a formal parameter of a method.
